name: Abstractive Grunge Glow
description:
[25-08-19]
Using superluminal.tv Stardustᵀᴹ plugin in After Effects to create abstract artsy grunge style. It was really fun trying different seed values and thinker with the nodes to obtain different results. Always fun discovering what it looks like when you change the values and the screen refreshes.
